io.github.eutro.jwasm.ExportsVisitor
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExportsNode, ExportsWriter
public class ExportsVisitor extends BaseVisitor<ExportsVisitor>
A visitor that visits the export section of a module.

Methods are expected to be called in the order:

( visitExport )* visitEnd

      Visit an export of a module.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the export.
      type - The type of the export, one of Opcodes.EXPORTS_FUNC, Opcodes.EXPORTS_TABLE, Opcodes.EXPORTS_MEM or Opcodes.EXPORTS_GLOBAL.
